{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/【配布あり・編集可能】Blenderでパチンコ文字/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://sititou70.github.io"}},"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"あけましておめでとうございます．sititou70です． 正月，実家でテレビを見ていて，以下のようなゴテゴテな文字が番組やCMによく使用されていると気づきました．  出典: 謹賀新年のテキスト素材 - Cafi Net 見ていて「なんかパチンコの演出みてぇだな」と思ったのでBlender…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 728px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/93a6d78e3d337876bd14cd02debe7e77/f8a3c/rend.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.31868131868132%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/93a6d78e3d337876bd14cd02debe7e77/f4a91/rend.webp 728w,\n/static/93a6d78e3d337876bd14cd02debe7e77/c58b7/rend.webp 1920w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/93a6d78e3d337876bd14cd02debe7e77/83881/rend.jpg 728w,\n/static/93a6d78e3d337876bd14cd02debe7e77/f8a3c/rend.jpg 1920w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/93a6d78e3d337876bd14cd02debe7e77/83881/rend.jpg\"\n            alt=\"レンダリング結果1\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>あけましておめでとうございます．sititou70です．</p>\n<p>正月，実家でテレビを見ていて，以下のようなゴテゴテな文字が番組やCMによく使用されていると気づきました．</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 460px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/43584a291cec4f6b619011a9f4e3b46d/9cab0/happy-new-year-sozai1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 28.695652173913043%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/43584a291cec4f6b619011a9f4e3b46d/aaa47/happy-new-year-sozai1.webp 460w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/43584a291cec4f6b619011a9f4e3b46d/9cab0/happy-new-year-sozai1.png 460w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/43584a291cec4f6b619011a9f4e3b46d/9cab0/happy-new-year-sozai1.png\"\n            alt=\"謹賀新年のテキスト素材\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>出典: <a href=\"https://japanism.info/happy-new-year-sozai.html\">謹賀新年のテキスト素材 - Cafi Net</a></p>\n<p>見ていて「なんかパチンコの演出みてぇだな」と思ったのでBlenderでパチンコ風文字を作ってみることにしました．</p>\n<h2 id=\"モデリング\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%83%A2%E3%83%87%E3%83%AA%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0\" aria-label=\"モデリング permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>モデリング</h2>\n<p>基本的には文字の押し出しやべべリングの設定をしていくだけなので簡単です．</p>\n<p>まずはテキストを打ちます．後々のマテリアルの設定を簡単にするため，「配置」の項目はどちらも「中心」にしておきます．「プレビュー解像度」は12くらいしておくと結果がきれいになります．</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 728px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a5725887a770ea63b21f652d82bdfd25/ff038/modeling01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.807692307692314%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a5725887a770ea63b21f652d82bdfd25/f4a91/modeling01.webp 728w,\n/static/a5725887a770ea63b21f652d82bdfd25/3a888/modeling01.webp 762w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a5725887a770ea63b21f652d82bdfd25/83881/modeling01.jpg 728w,\n/static/a5725887a770ea63b21f652d82bdfd25/ff038/modeling01.jpg 762w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a5725887a770ea63b21f652d82bdfd25/83881/modeling01.jpg\"\n            alt=\"文字のモデリング1\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>文字サイズを7くらいに設定し，1mくらい押し出します．</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 728px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/84cb37bee09f37c6093d663b3e43ba64/8ebbb/modeling02.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.065934065934066%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/84cb37bee09f37c6093d663b3e43ba64/f4a91/modeling02.webp 728w,\n/static/84cb37bee09f37c6093d663b3e43ba64/01257/modeling02.webp 871w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/84cb37bee09f37c6093d663b3e43ba64/83881/modeling02.jpg 728w,\n/static/84cb37bee09f37c6093d663b3e43ba64/8ebbb/modeling02.jpg 871w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/84cb37bee09f37c6093d663b3e43ba64/83881/modeling02.jpg\"\n            alt=\"文字のモデリング2\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>「ベベル」を「断面」モードに設定し，深度は1.5mくらい，解像度は最高の32，プリセットから「コーニスモールディング」を選択します．さらに，「真っ直ぐな辺を取得」と「均一な長さを取得」という謎の項目を有効にすると，心なしかモデルがバグりづらくなります．</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 728px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f9b8cdb73f933994b612b11b44ae276b/56a08/modeling03.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.59890109890111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f9b8cdb73f933994b612b11b44ae276b/f4a91/modeling03.webp 728w,\n/static/f9b8cdb73f933994b612b11b44ae276b/8bc45/modeling03.webp 855w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f9b8cdb73f933994b612b11b44ae276b/83881/modeling03.jpg 728w,\n/static/f9b8cdb73f933994b612b11b44ae276b/56a08/modeling03.jpg 855w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f9b8cdb73f933994b612b11b44ae276b/83881/modeling03.jpg\"\n            alt=\"文字のモデリング3\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>これでモデルは基本的に完成です．お好みでフォントを変更したり，カーニングしたりしてください．</p>\n<h2 id=\"マテリアルの設定\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%83%9E%E3%83%86%E3%83%AA%E3%82%A2%E3%83%AB%E3%81%AE%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A\" aria-label=\"マテリアルの設定 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>マテリアルの設定</h2>\n<p>テキストをメッシュへ変換せずにどうやってマテリアルを振り分けるのか？というのが一番の関門です．</p>\n<p>このブログで毎度使っている手法ですが，「テクスチャ座標 -> オブジェクト」からテクスチャのローカル位置ベクトルが得られます．したがって，そのx座標の絶対値を使ってマテリアルのベースカラーを切り替えれば良さそうです．</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 414px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1ff150303d5816927fa8524a1beb472d/db571/material01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 150.2415458937198%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/1ff150303d5816927fa8524a1beb472d/9c87f/material01.webp 414w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 100vw, 414px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/1ff150303d5816927fa8524a1beb472d/db571/material01.jpg 414w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 100vw, 414px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/1ff150303d5816927fa8524a1beb472d/db571/material01.jpg\"\n            alt=\"マテリアル1\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>この0〜1の値によって色を切り替えるノードグループを次のように作成しました．</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 728px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/85384a3d0b62752e1d3493da681740bd/91595/material02.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.76373626373626%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/85384a3d0b62752e1d3493da681740bd/f4a91/material02.webp 728w,\n/static/85384a3d0b62752e1d3493da681740bd/a0641/material02.webp 939w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/85384a3d0b62752e1d3493da681740bd/83881/material02.jpg 728w,\n/static/85384a3d0b62752e1d3493da681740bd/91595/material02.jpg 939w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/85384a3d0b62752e1d3493da681740bd/83881/material02.jpg\"\n            alt=\"マテリアル2\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>このノードグループを使って全体のノードを組むと次のようになります．意外とシンプルですね．</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 728px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/881399782a39a28f47a901473ebc696a/7af55/material03.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.14835164835165%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/881399782a39a28f47a901473ebc696a/f4a91/material03.webp 728w,\n/static/881399782a39a28f47a901473ebc696a/57e40/material03.webp 1079w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/881399782a39a28f47a901473ebc696a/83881/material03.jpg 728w,\n/static/881399782a39a28f47a901473ebc696a/7af55/material03.jpg 1079w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/881399782a39a28f47a901473ebc696a/83881/material03.jpg\"\n            alt=\"マテリアル3\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>なお，一番手前の色は少し凝った作りになっています．全体は2色のグラデーションになっていて，それをグラデーションテクスチャによって斜めにグラデーションさせています．また，グラデーションの中心部分の色相を，ボロノイテクスチャの値でバラけさせています．こうすることで，なんかいいかんじになります．</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 728px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f5f5d1d75927eb3656dca45f8926bc30/31c86/material04.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.65384615384615%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f5f5d1d75927eb3656dca45f8926bc30/f4a91/material04.webp 728w,\n/static/f5f5d1d75927eb3656dca45f8926bc30/69828/material04.webp 1286w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f5f5d1d75927eb3656dca45f8926bc30/83881/material04.jpg 728w,\n/static/f5f5d1d75927eb3656dca45f8926bc30/31c86/material04.jpg 1286w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f5f5d1d75927eb3656dca45f8926bc30/83881/material04.jpg\"\n            alt=\"マテリアル4\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"完成\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90\" aria-label=\"完成 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>完成</h2>\n<p>↓CR年賀状．</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 